## ğŸ¤ Putting It All Together: The Symbiosis

Can you use controls and skip the framework?  
Technically, yesâ€”but itâ€™s risky. Without a framework, security becomes reactive; just plugging holes as they appear.

The *framework* gives a holistic view of risk (legal, financial, reputational).  
*Controls* put risk mitigation into action.

